high_descs: Turn around and walk through the kitchen over to the round white table
Pick up the tomato by the spatula from the table
Turn around and walk back over to the microwave above the stove
Put the tomato in the microwave, cook it, and remove it
Turn around and walk back over to the round white table
Put the tomato on the table just right of the butter knife
anns.task_desc: Put the cooked tomato on the round table

high_descs: Move to the table to the left of the stove
Pick up a tomato from the table
Move to the microwave behind you
Heat the tomato inside the microwave
Move to the table behind you
Put the tomato on the desk
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn around, go straight toward the wall, turn right, then turn left to face the table.
Pick up the rightmost tomato on the table.
Turn left, move forward, turn left, move forward, turn left, then turn right to approach the microwave.
Heat the tomato in the microwave.
Turn right, move forward, turn right, go forward to pass the counter, then turn right, move forward, then turn left to face the table.
Place the tomato on the table, in between the knife and the potato.
anns.task_desc: Put a warm tomato on the table.
